FSRI: Dimensions: 99.46 x 99.21 x 39.63 mm; with frame and grid

A few seconds prior to ignition the laminate inflated, then popped violently, causing a spike in mass data. The inflation of the laminate pushed the wire grid upwards, approaching the spark ignitor. The flames extinguished at around 2:50. The spark ignitor was reinserted, and reignition occurred at around 8:45. Test ended after 60 minutes, per ASTM criteria.
